quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  43,16,"What, has He taken daughters out of what He Himself creates, and given sons to you"
  43,17,"When news is brought to one of them of the birth of what he attributes to God, the Merciful Benefactor, his face darkens, and he is filled with inward grief"
  43,18,"One who is to be reared to be a trophy, and finds themselves torn by inner conflict"
  43,19,"And they created into females, angels who themselves serve God. Did they witness their creation? Their evidence will be recorded, and they will be called to account"
  43,20,"They say, “If it had been the will of God, the Merciful Benefactor, we would not have worshipped such deities.” They have no knowledge of that, they do nothing but lie"
  43,21,"What, have We given them a book before this, to which they hold fast"
  43,22,"No, they say, “We found our fathers following a certain way, and we guide ourselves by their footsteps.”"
  43,23,"In the same way that when We sent a warner before you to any people, the elite among them said, “We found our fathers following a certain way, and we will certainly follow in their footsteps.”"
  43,24,"He said, “What, even if I brought you better guidance than that which you found your fathers following?” They said, “For us, we deny that you are sent on a mission at all.”"
  43,25,So We took retribution from them. Now see what the end of those who rejected it was